OL,7,FThe chief of the Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fhas suggested the law may need
OL,9,Ftightening after his force decided a
OL,10,Fvideo of a man chanting "Jihad" at a
OL,11,Fpro-Palestine protest on Saturday did
OL,12,Fnot show any offence being committed.
OL,14,FSir Mark Rowley, following a meeting
OL,15,Fwith the home secretary in which he
OL,16,Fwas told officers must "use the full
OL,17,Fforce of the law" at protests, said
OL,18,Frecent events may have shown the need
OL,19,Ffor new legislation.
OL,3,CMet chief suggests law needs
OL,4,Ctightening after lack of action on
OL,5,C'Jihad' chant video
